# ConfigLoaderSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
One-shot initialization system for SandboxApp. On the first frame, reads
`Assets/App/Config.json` and creates SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent containing the UUIDs for
the two UI elements, the default font, and the main UI layout. No-op on all subsequent frames
(presence check guards early exit).

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent | read | Presence-check only; if present, system exits immediately |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent | add (deferred) | Created once from Assets/App/Config.json; holds four UUIDs |
